[10.415, "o", "\u001b[38;5;209m\u273b\u001b[0m \u001b[2mWorking\u2026 (esc to interrupt \u00b7 3h 40m \u00b7 \u2193 61.2k tokens)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[12.235, "o", "\r\n"]
[12.535, "o", "\u001b[2;33m\u29c9 context injected by claude-powernap hook:\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[12.785, "o", "\u001b[33m  USAGE LIMIT WARNING: you have consumed 91% of the 5-hour usage window.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[12.985, "o", "\u001b[33m  The window resets at 2026-07-18 03:00AM EDT. At the current burn rate the\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[13.185, "o", "\u001b[33m  limit is ~8 minutes away. To avoid dying mid-task, follow this pause\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[13.385, "o", "\u001b[33m  protocol NOW: 1. Do NOT start new work\u2026 2. Write a checkpoint file\u2026\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[15.505, "o", "\r\n"]
[15.755, "o", "\u23fa I'm at 91% of the session window \u2014 pausing gracefully instead of dying\r\n"]
[15.875, "o", "  mid-migration. Billing module is done and green; checkpointing here.\r\n"]
